{"title":"Stinner Refugio Select","link":"https://theradavist.com/stinner-refugio-select/","date":1736859634000,"content":"<p><em>Today, California’s <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/tag/stinner-frameworks/\" target=\"_blank\">Stinner Frameworks</a> announces an expansion to its Select program with the Refugio Select, offering another stock bike model at a more affordable price point. Let’s check out this capable 700 x 50 mm gravel platform’s offerings…</em><span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Refugio-Select-10.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Refugio-Select-10.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Refugio-Select-10.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Refugio-Select-10.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Refugio-Select-7.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Refugio-Select-7.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Refugio-Select-7.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Refugio-Select-7.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<h3>Refugio Select Gravel Bike</h3>\n<p>The <a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;merchant_id=1f9a8274-6211-42cc-bc96-aec25cc460f4&amp;website_id=6ec3743b-a948-4c16-9d12-4b79ac107f25&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.stinnerframeworks.com%2Fproducts%2Frefugio-select\" target=\"_blank\">Refugio Select</a> embodies the spirit of adventure and challenge, drawing inspiration from the rugged, winding terrain of Refugio Road in Santa Barbara, CA, home of Stinner Frameworks. It is designed for versatility and endurance, thriving on all surfaces, from steep climbs to rough descents.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Refugio-Select-6.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Refugio-Select-6.jpg?w=200&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Refugio-Select-6.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Refugio-Select-5.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Refugio-Select-5.jpg?w=200&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Refugio-Select-5.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Refugio-Select-4.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Refugio-Select-4.jpg?w=200&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Refugio-Select-4.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Refugio-Select-1.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Refugio-Select-1.jpg?w=200&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Refugio-Select-1.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>Now available as part of the Stiner Select line, the Columbus Zona/Life tubing blend offers a responsive and smooth ride, built to handle even the most challenging routes. Every Refugio Select is fabricated, painted, and assembled in Santa Barbara, CA, with clearance for 50 mm tires, UDH compatibility, and a component package prioritizing reliability and serviceability.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Refugio-Select-8.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Refugio-Select-8.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Refugio-Select-8.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Refugio-Select-8.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Refugio-Select-GEO.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Refugio-Select-GEO.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Refugio-Select-GEO.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Refugio-Select-GEO.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<h3>Geometry</h3>\n<p>Some notable integers are the healthy stack numbers and a size-specific geometry. Each size Refugio Select is meant to optimize the ride quality for its owner, no matter their frame size.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Refugio-Select-2.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Refugio-Select-2.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Refugio-Select-2.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Refugio-Select-2.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Refugio-Select-9.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Refugio-Select-9.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Refugio-Select-9.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Refugio-Select-9.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Refugio-Select-7.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Refugio-Select-7.jpg?w=300&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Refugio-Select-7.jpg?w=600&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2025/01/Stinner-Refugio-Select-7.jpg?w=800&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<h3>Refugio Select Quick Hits:</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Material // Columbus Zona/Life Steel Tube Set</li>\n<li>Finish // Durable Powder Coat</li>\n<li>Dropouts // Stinner UDH 160mm Flat Mount Steel Dropouts</li>\n<li>Drivetrain Compatibility // Mechanical 1x (External full length housing) / SRAM AXS – Transmission/Full Mount compatible</li>\n<li>MAX Tire Clearance // 700 x 50mm</li>\n<li>MAX Tire Clearance w/ Fenders // 700 x 45mm</li>\n<li>MAX Chainring Clearance // 1x: 42t (47.5mm chainline)</li>\n<li>Dropout Spacing // 142 x 12mm</li>\n<li>Rear Axle // 166mm – M12 x 1.0 – 15mm threaded portion</li>\n<li>Brake Mount // Flat Mount 160mm</li>\n<li>MAX Rotor Size // 160mm</li>\n<li>Brake Routing // External w/bolt-on and zip-tie guides</li>\n<li>Seatpost Diameter // 27.2mm</li>\n<li>Seatpost Clamp Diameter // 30mm</li>\n<li>Bottom Bracket // BSA 68mm wide shell</li>\n<li>Headtube Diameter // 44mm Internal Top and Bottom</li>\n<li>Headset Specs // Upper: ZS44/28.6 – Lower: EC44/40</li>\n<li>Mounts // Fender Mounts – 3 bottle cage locations</li>\n</ul>\n<p>See more at <a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;merchant_id=1f9a8274-6211-42cc-bc96-aec25cc460f4&amp;website_id=6ec3743b-a948-4c16-9d12-4b79ac107f25&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.stinnerframeworks.com%2Fproducts%2Frefugio-select\" target=\"_blank\">Stinner Frameworks</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/stinner-refugio-select/\">Stinner Refugio Select</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"da46b0f7f79ba2713ef10a6280210b461f49694bc5bd0ca81eaa67ae9ac64234","category":"Cycling"}